{"tid":1681350,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"數學題 獨派人數是至少八十萬人 ！進取啲亦有一百三十萬啊人！","createTime":"2019-10-29T11:06:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T12:18:36.000Z","uid":167548,"like":21,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"9b3cc3874ecc040854ed67200c35ba107f925ba2","tid":1681350,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T11:06:22.000Z","msg":"政府統計處統計2019年年中香港人口臨時數字，香港人口數字首次突破<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">750萬</span></strong>，較2018年中的745萬人口來比，共錄得73,100人增長，增長率為1%。 當中人口自然增長（即出生減死亡）達5,700人，出生人數為53,300人，死亡人數為47,600人。<br />\n<br />\nSource:支那01<br />\n<br />\n數學題 支持港獨 11% + 半獨派 6%<br />\n<br />\n進取啲估計：750&times;0.17=127.5萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n保定啲估計：750&times;0.11=82.5萬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n簡單啲講就是極深黃手足有130萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n下次記得見人就講獨派有130萬人,<br />\n<br />\n利用吸引力法則講, 慢慢獨派就會成為不用說出口的主流民意<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 場運動持續更耐, 只會更想獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個情況就是你地昔日個個幻想自己條邨/區好深藍㗎啦,建制當道<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但是投票率得40%<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋你地可唔可以唔好再自己用埋沉默大多數嘅理論<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />事實上香港有好多自稱黃嘅freerider(保守遊行參與者達200萬), 同埋班死鬼藍屍wfc<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你地要明白唔出聲嘅就理得佢啦！<br />\n<br />\n你相信香港可以獨立, 去感染其他人！<br />\n<br />\n肯發聲嘅陪我地行落去嘅先是我地在乎嘅！<br />\n倘若黃絲手足全部是獨派, 做咩都撚割,<br />\n獨立就是要血！汗！動亂！死人！割狗！<br />\n<br />\n利申港獨在心中<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n但是我屌你老母, 做民調唔夠膽講支持怕被抄名, 最起碼話自己十五十六啦！ </span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\n我要獨立！<br />\n<br />\n完！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"ea71a87a2480c920994483448de1390deba04601","tid":1681350,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T11:07:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T7kDwBC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT7kDwBC.jpg&h=6da1c92c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mtm3RDU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMtm3RDU.jpg&h=fd9c9c47&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"ab869ab820f031e1fe475d2efeaa851339c9f1d1","tid":1681350,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T11:07:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81dcd0f76fa6204ca502176438728616a4566237","tid":1681350,"uid":167548,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T11:08:58.000Z","msg":"We want democracy, autonomy, independence！Fuck You CCP！But we wouldn't say it now！"},{"pid":"626ccbd2de9fdc7b76d885084fc834ef28fb2188","tid":1681350,"uid":69221,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T11:09:32.000Z","msg":"梁天琦：呢四個字我好想講，但係要參選唔講得<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/opCnp55.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FopCnp55.png&h=52037ebf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"222cce28433b3660180f250bd2c2c7a638aab08a","tid":1681350,"uid":167548,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T11:10:04.000Z","msg":"唔好再學埋啲沉默大多數理論<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n企出嚟嘅手足大部分是獨派<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8339d5457482d3269d4eaeb4a5bda21963311afd","tid":1681350,"uid":2260,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T11:10:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b823f262d43ed0c755703ec4cefd42d493d911c7","tid":1681350,"uid":69221,"like":